data.text/markdown: Data Manipulation

Total Charges vs Monthly Charges

I assumed that Total Charges was an interaction between Monthly Charges X Tenure. However the difference between the assumed interaction and the Total Charges value are too far apart to assume that the assumption holds.
Checking Values
Hist plots of all columns
Hist plots comparing Churn vs Not Churn
Correlation Heatmap

Tenure

Months being a customer

Services

All the services have 3 values: Yes, No, No internet service Can we change "No internet service" to "No" with minimal effect?

Charges

There must be multicolinearity between Total Charges and Tenure * Monthly Charges
